column2: The Great Mali Comes Back Again!
Mali was once the richest nation in Earth, now, with our nation united yet again we sahll surpass greater heights then ever achieved before! Mali Forever!

We have proven our mettle and united the Iberian peninsula under our rule. Now the time has come for a new Iberian federation to be born, one that unites all of the peninsula's cultures under a single rule.
We 've finally managed to unite the nether realms, now it's time to show the world our might!
Put the frogs under our soles!
It has come the time to bring them to the fold again, we shall rise once more with the frogs under our banner!
